item.title: Moab Videos Uploaded
item.description: I have been wanting to do this for a while, and finally got around to it. I have uploaded 2009, 2010, 2011, and 2012 Moab Videos to my YouTube Channel. Sadly, 2015 will not happen this year, but we are planning on 2016 trip. 2016 should be epic as we have some surprises planned for that year!
